{"4282720": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "頹廢！！兔子性活", "steam_appid": 4282720, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/3b6feea74bf9232faa8ec2f7ebee4b52.poster.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/3b6feea74bf9232faa8ec2f7ebee4b52.webm?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/3b6feea74bf9232faa8ec2f7ebee4b52.mp4?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【故事劇情】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與頹廢兔子的開心色情性活♪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是兔子「小樂子」的飼主。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一邊守護著「小樂子」朝著月亮跳躍、進行打工，一邊一起出門約會、享受H事件吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲特徵】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/5e9644a0ce06e5a2d962c69b430852aa.poster.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/5e9644a0ce06e5a2d962c69b430852aa.webm?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/5e9644a0ce06e5a2d962c69b430852aa.mp4?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過unity動畫製作的甜蜜蜜H事件♪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然不如live2d那麼細緻，不過透過unity的動畫功能製作的H事件，也非常值得一看。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以變更H事件的再生速度、以及開啟關閉對話框。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >（回想模式時）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【遊戲內容】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/514a604699232152d75b3aa98b9a5bba.poster.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/514a604699232152d75b3aa98b9a5bba.webm?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/514a604699232152d75b3aa98b9a5bba.mp4?t=1776160140\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >紀念兔年的遊戲終於完成……！（現在才嗎）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因為是兔子（？），所以跳躍到月亮上便是這個遊戲的目標。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然會看反射神經跟運氣，但只要拼命訓練提升狀態的話就能做到，就算不擅長也儘管放心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/cf520723afe86d92b5e76bd8a32299c9.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了賺到約會的費用，滿懷幹勁地努力工作吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用跳躍接連踩上上方的立足點，收集大量的硬幣吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/abfecd4a0ad82965a55b247f7b826335.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=390 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了跳得更高更遠，色色的鍛鍊是必不可少的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鍛鍊會影響打工以及以月亮為目標的結果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/836163aa291240e13f705686d10d2a39.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >賺到硬幣的話，就花費在開心的約會上吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與謎之貓耳少女相遇、宛如地獄的兜風、出現暴露狂、還有可能會被宇宙人給抓走……！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >既開心又色情的事件豐富多樣♪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【角色】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/d3055a630187687fcee245563903dc28.avif?t=1776160140\" width=300 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆小樂子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事女主角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在還是小兔子的時候被主人收養，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雖然胸部發育得又大又豐滿，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但因為一直過著頹廢的生活，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最終導致她的態度也變得囂張不已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/b199c9a5e3cacef4142eea70cd3a7d8c.avif?t=1776160140\" width=300 height=407 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆貓耳暗殺少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好像有在哪裡見過的貓耳少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以暗殺為生（自稱），武器是竹輪刀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >好像在尋找自己的冒牌貨……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/f3d473f25f70378b281c836577373862.avif?t=1776160140\" width=300 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆菜美江</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >兔子導覽員的彩美江小姐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因為奶子太大，所以平常總是會露出奶子來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她一直都處在發情狀態中，還請務必小心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4282720/extras/3b6feea74bf9232faa8ec2f7ebee4b52.poster.avif?t=1776160140\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as